confidence: high
resolution: Made list pagination keys stable and omitted unset filter echoes from the serialized result envelope.
expected_result: "Every list JSON result carries total, has_more, truncated, and next_cursor without null-heavy filter bloat."
actual_result: Stable keys pass runtime ordering coverage and the measured list-json budget dropped from 1307 to 828 bytes.
